","text":"The LORD hath sworn, and will not repent, Thou art a priest for ever after the order of Melchizedek.","year":-1042},{"id":"recRpW0Zz0U4bzuOU","ref":"Ps.110.5","text":"The Lord at thy right hand shall strike through kings in the day of his wrath.","year":-1042},{"id":"recrUA1WXv3pnI6bi","ref":"Ps.110.6","text":"He shall judge among the heathen, he shall fill the places with the dead bodies; he shall wound the heads over many countries.","year":-1042},{"id":"recATdKRGCUhMoeQc","ref":"Ps.110.7","text":"He shall drink of the brook in the way: therefore shall he lift up the head.","year":-1042}]}
